陣列原本嚴格遞增，在某個未知位置旋轉（例如 `[4,5,6,7,0,1,2]`）。在其中搜尋 `target`，無重複元素。

```cpp
int searchRotated(const vector<int>& a, int target) {
    int lo = 0, hi = (int)a.size() - 1;
    while (lo <= hi) {
        int mid = lo + (hi - lo) / 2;
        if (a[mid] == target)
            return mid;
        if (a[lo] <= a[mid]) {  // Left half [lo, mid] is sorted
            if (a[lo] <= target && target < a[mid])
                hi = mid - 1;  // Target falls in the sorted left half
            else
                lo = mid + 1;  // Target must be in the right half
        } else {               // Right half [mid, hi] is sorted
            if (a[mid] < target && target <= a[hi])
                lo = mid + 1;  // Target falls in the sorted right half
            else
                hi = mid - 1;  // Target must be in the left half
        }
    }
    return -1;  // Not found
}
```

判斷左半有序用 `a[lo] <= a[mid]`（含等號以處理 `lo == mid` 的兩元素區間）。確認 target 落在有序那半的閉區間值域後再縮範圍，否則去另一半。若陣列含重複元素，`a[lo] == a[mid]` 時無法判斷，需退化為 `lo++` 線性跳過，最壞 O(n)。

給定相鄰元素皆不相等的陣列（邊界外視為 -∞），找出任意一個峰值元素的下標（峰值：嚴格大於兩側相鄰元素）。

```cpp
int findPeak(const vector<int>& a) {
    int lo = 0, hi = (int)a.size() - 1;
    while (lo < hi) {
        int mid = lo + (hi - lo) / 2;
        if (a[mid] < a[mid + 1])
            lo = mid + 1;  // Ascending: peak must be to the right of mid
        else
            hi = mid;  // Descending (a[mid] > a[mid+1]): peak is at mid or to its left
    }
    return lo;  // Invariant guarantees lo == hi is a peak
}
```

**不變式**：`[lo, hi]` 內必有峰值。若 `a[mid] < a[mid+1]`，`mid+1` 比 `mid` 高且 `hi` 外側為 -∞，故 `[mid+1, hi]` 必有峰值，令 `lo = mid + 1`；若 `a[mid] > a[mid+1]`，`a[mid]` 比右側高且 `lo` 外側為 -∞，故 `[lo, mid]` 必有峰值，令 `hi = mid`。注意 `hi = mid`（非 `mid - 1`）——`a[mid]` 本身可能就是峰值，不能丟棄。

template_code:
// Search in rotated sorted array (no duplicates), returns index or -1
int searchRotated(const vector<int>& a, int target) {
    int lo = 0, hi = (int)a.size() - 1;
    while (lo <= hi) {
        int mid = lo + (hi - lo) / 2;
        if (a[mid] == target)
            return mid;
        if (a[lo] <= a[mid]) {  // Left half [lo, mid] sorted
            if (a[lo] <= target && target < a[mid])
                hi = mid - 1;
            else
                lo = mid + 1;
        } else {  // Right half [mid, hi] sorted
            if (a[mid] < target && target <= a[hi])
                lo = mid + 1;
            else
                hi = mid - 1;
        }
    }
    return -1;
}

// Find any peak element index (adjacent elements are distinct)
int findPeak(const vector<int>& a) {
    int lo = 0, hi = (int)a.size() - 1;
    while (lo < hi) {
        int mid = lo + (hi - lo) / 2;
        if (a[mid] < a[mid + 1])
            lo = mid + 1;  // Ascending slope: go right
        else
            hi = mid;  // Descending slope: peak at mid or left
    }
    return lo;
}

