函數定義在整數點上，值嚴格單峰，求極大值所在下標。

```cpp
// f(x) is a user-supplied strictly unimodal function on integers
// Returns the x in [lo, hi] that maximizes f(x)
long long ternarySearchInt(long long lo, long long hi) {
    while (hi - lo > 2) {  // Stop when at most 3 candidates remain
        long long m1 = lo + (hi - lo) / 3;
        long long m2 = hi - (hi - lo) / 3;
        if (f(m1) < f(m2))
            lo = m1 + 1;  // Peak cannot be in [lo, m1]: eliminate left third
        else
            hi = m2 - 1;  // Peak cannot be in [m2, hi]: eliminate right third
    }
    // Brute-force the remaining small interval (at most 3 points)
    long long best = lo;
    for (long long x = lo + 1; x <= hi; x++)
        if (f(x) > f(best))
            best = x;
    return best;
}
```

整數三分以 `hi - lo > 2` 為迴圈條件，剩餘不超過 3 個候選點時直接枚舉，避免邊界複雜性。若求**極小值**（嚴格單谷），只需把 `f(m1) < f(m2)` 改成 `f(m1) > f(m2)`，移動方向相同，語意對調。

函數定義在實數上（如幾何最短距離、物理拋物線問題），求極值的近似位置。

```cpp
// f(x) is a user-supplied strictly unimodal real function
// Returns the approximate x in [lo, hi] that maximizes f(x)
double ternarySearchReal(double lo, double hi) {
    const int kIter = 200;  // (2/3)^200 ~ 1e-35: far exceeds double precision
    for (int i = 0; i < kIter; i++) {
        double m1 = lo + (hi - lo) / 3.0;
        double m2 = hi - (hi - lo) / 3.0;
        if (f(m1) < f(m2))
            lo = m1;  // Peak in [m1, hi]
        else
            hi = m2;  // Peak in [lo, m2]
    }
    return (lo + hi) / 2.0;  // Midpoint of the converged interval
}
```

實數版不需 `+1`/`-1`，直接用浮點 `m1`、`m2` 更新邊界。迭代 200 次後區間縮小為原來的 `(2/3)^200 ≈ 10^{-35}` 倍，遠超雙精度需求。避免使用 `while (hi - lo > EPS)` — EPS 設太大會提早停止，設太小可能因浮點誤差造成無窮迴圈。

