以**最長無重複字元子字串**（LeetCode 3）示範「最長」模板，以**最短覆蓋子字串**（LeetCode 76）示範「最短」模板：

```cpp
// Longest substring without repeating characters (LeetCode 3)
int lengthOfLongestSubstring(const string& s) {
    int n = s.size(), ans = 0, left = 0;
    unordered_map<char, int> freq;
    for (int right = 0; right < n; right++) {
        freq[s[right]]++;
        while (freq[s[right]] > 1) {  // Window invalid: duplicate exists
            if (--freq[s[left]] == 0)
                freq.erase(s[left]);
            left++;
        }
        ans = max(ans, right - left + 1);  // Update after shrinking
    }
    return ans;
}

// Minimum window substring (LeetCode 76)
string minWindow(const string& s, const string& t) {
    unordered_map<char, int> need, have;
    for (char c : t)
        need[c]++;
    int formed = 0, required = (int)need.size();
    int left = 0, min_len = INT_MAX, min_start = 0;
    for (int right = 0; right < (int)s.size(); right++) {
        have[s[right]]++;
        // Check if this character type is now fully covered
        if (need.count(s[right]) && have[s[right]] == need[s[right]])
            formed++;
        while (formed == required) {  // Window valid: try shrinking
            if (right - left + 1 < min_len) {
                min_len = right - left + 1;
                min_start = left;
            }
            if (need.count(s[left]) && --have[s[left]] < need[s[left]])
                formed--;
            else
                have[s[left]]--;
            left++;
        }
    }
    return min_len == INT_MAX ? "" : s.substr(min_start, min_len);
}
```

**最長**：先擴張 `right`，不合法時縮左，合法後更新答案（答案在循環末尾更新）。**最短**：擴張直到合法，然後在 while 內持續縮左並更新答案，離開 while 後視窗恢復不合法狀態。

`atMost(k)` 統計每個 `right` 對應的合法起點數量（即以 `right` 結尾、以 `[left..right]` 內任一點為起點的合法子陣列數 `right - left + 1`），累加即得所有「最多 K 個不同值」的子陣列數。`atMost(K) - atMost(K-1)` 容斥得「恰好 K 個」：

```cpp
// Count subarrays with at most k distinct integers
int atMost(const vector<int>& a, int k) {
    if (k < 0)
        return 0;  // Guard for atMost(-1) call
    int n = a.size(), left = 0, ans = 0;
    unordered_map<int, int> freq;
    for (int right = 0; right < n; right++) {
        freq[a[right]]++;
        while ((int)freq.size() > k) {  // Too many distinct values
            if (--freq[a[left]] == 0)
                freq.erase(a[left]);
            left++;
        }
        ans += right - left + 1;  // All subarrays ending at right are valid
    }
    return ans;
}

// Count subarrays with exactly k distinct integers (LeetCode 992)
int exactlyK(const vector<int>& a, int k) {
    return atMost(a, k) - atMost(a, k - 1);
}
```

此技巧適用於所有「恰好 K 次滿足某條件」且可轉化為「最多」計數的問題，例如「恰好 K 個奇數的子陣列」、「恰好翻轉 K 次的子字串」等。

